---
// Accomplishments / Feature Gallery section
// Adapted from Figma export -- three card types: metric-dark, metric-light, headline
---

<section class="accomplishments-section">
  <div class="accomplishments-inner">
    <h2 class="accomplishments-title">Recent accomplishments</h2>
    <div class="gallery">

      <!-- Column 1 -->
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card spacer"></div>

        <div class="card metric-light">
          <p class="metric-number">500%</p>
          <p class="metric-label">Team growth</p>
          <p class="card-body">Grew the team from 7 to over 35 product and content designers in two years. Along the way, shifted the culture from ticket takers to strategic partners.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card headline-neutral">
          <p class="headline-title">Built Company-Wide Design System</p>
          <p class="card-body">Defined the vision and led MoxiWorks' first design system from zero, earning dedicated engineering resources and bringing consistency to a product that had none.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card headline-neutral">
          <p class="headline-title">Redefined coverage transparency</p>
          <p class="card-body">Coverage maps are typically built for marketing, not customers. We rebuilt ours around accuracy, prioritizing trust in the areas where churn was highest.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card metric-light">
          <p class="metric-number">19k</p>
          <p class="metric-label">Activations</p>
          <p class="card-body">Led an agency to design a carrier switching experience built directly into our existing app. Removing that friction resulted in 19,000 new activations in year one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2 -->
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card headline-neutral">
          <p class="headline-title">Modernized the authenticated experience</p>
          <p class="card-body">Led redesign of 85% of authenticated journeys during platform migration, achieving full accessibility compliance and measurable customer satisfaction gains.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card headline-light">
          <p class="headline-title">AI Product Design Certification</p>
          <p class="card-body">Completed advanced AI product design training with formal recommendation, applying machine learning concepts and ethical principles to product strategy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card headline-neutral">
          <p class="headline-title">Biometric pre-authentication patent</p>
          <p class="card-body">Co-invented and patented a biometric pre-authentication system that made customer care faster, more secure, and more seamless.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 3 -->
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card spacer"></div>

        <div class="card headline-neutral">
          <p class="headline-title">Built foundations team from scratch</p>
          <p class="card-body">Established and scaled a Foundations team to own navigation, onboarding, authentication, notifications, and other critical experience systems.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card metric-light">
          <p class="metric-number">59%</p>
          <p class="metric-label">Share of enterprise</p>
          <p class="card-body">Oversaw the team that hit a record 59% share of enterprise and processed 276,000 digital device orders during Apple's iPhone launch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card headline-neutral">
          <p class="headline-title">Safety-first infotainment design</p>
          <p class="card-body">Designed infotainment for real driving conditions, testing interactions in simulators to balance safety with staying connected.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card companies">
          <p class="companies-title">Organizations I've partnered with</p>
          <ul class="companies-list">
            <li>T-Mobile</li>
            <li>Apple</li>
            <li>AT&T</li>
            <li>MoxiWorks</li>
            <li>Mapbox</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .accomplishments-section {
    background: #ffffff;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .accomplishments-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 56px;
  }

  .accomplishments-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #2b2b2b;
    margin: 0 0 48px 0;
  }

  /* ── GALLERY GRID ── */
  .gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  /* ── CARD BASE ── */
  .card {
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px 30px;
  }

  .card.spacer {
    background: #ffffff;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* ── METRIC CARDS ── */
  .metric-number {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 48px 0;
  }

  .card-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 21px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card.metric-dark {
    background: #2b2b2b;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .card.metric-light {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e0dfdf;
    color: #2b2b2b;
  }

  /* ── HEADLINE CARDS ── */
  .headline-title {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0 0 48px 0;
    color: #2b2b2b;
  }

  .card.headline-neutral {
    background: #F5F4F0;
    color: #2b2b2b;
    padding: 48px 30px;
  }

  .card.headline-light {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e0dfdf;
    color: #2b2b2b;
    padding: 48px 30px;
  }

  /* ── COMPANIES CARD ── */
  .card.companies {
    background: #2b2b2b;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 28px 30px 40px;
  }

  .companies-title {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 32px 0;
  }

  .companies-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px 24px;
  }

  .companies-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .col {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .card.spacer {
      display: none;
    }

    .accomplishments-inner {
      padding: 60px 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
